{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act39side", "eventName": "出蒼白海", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EP-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "傾瀉腐朽的花", "storyInfo": "棘刺再次開始修復羅盤，而逃向峽谷的眾人不知明日會怎樣。鎮子中，為雅隆鎮操勞一生的西爾弗，被再次復活的安納斯塔西奧認為生出了不該有的慾望，最終為其所殺。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g8_oldcabin", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenship_cabin", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽落了下去，鹽漠的晚上冷到所有人都在顫抖。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家翻遍了破落的船艙，才勉強找到了一些不知放了多久的鱗肉乾和一口破鍋。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在仿生海龍的幫助下，鍋中終於有了一點熱氣。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dishes", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plateplace", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太冷了……之前那些碎木頭沒撐多久，就都已經燒完了，我讓小葉先來代替一下火盆吧。", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是本來它的加熱功能是用來暖手的，如果是烹煮食物的話，只能做到這種程度了……", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能吃到熱的已經很偉大了！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食物和淡水都不多，就算省著吃，這些也只能撐個兩三天。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是遇到雨雲，把集雨用的布袋放出去，大概還能再收回來一點水……但鹽漠裡的天氣向來難以預料。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面噴發的那些蒸汽……不能當作水源嗎？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#10$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡面混雜著鹽漠深處的微生物，人不能直接喝。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以過濾。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先修復羅盤。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我們先熬過今晚再說吧。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鹽漠深處的夜晚可不是鬧著玩的，吃的本來就不夠，有人還受了傷，不好好保暖的話，小心睡著睡著人就再也醒不過來了。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真的……真的會再也醒不過來了嗎？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是現在再遇上鹽鱗，我們可能真的就……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#3$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我可以發揮一下專長，先傳訊息給鹽鱗，就說我們來了，讓牠們準備乖乖受死。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我真的不懂，你為什麼不管什麼時候都能這麼無所謂？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#5$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "溫蒂", "content": "……忍忍吧，這個時候也就他會耍嘴皮子了……"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "溫蒂", "content": "啊，小心！"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_planeshake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎是壓過了一條骸骨，征服宣告號顛簸了起來，破鍋與裡面的食物一同被震飛。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境立刻跳起衝上前去接鍋，卻被燙得哀嚎。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多墊步上前，劍尖精準地穿過鍋的把手，這才勉強保住晚餐。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旁，仿生海龍的熱氣也消散了。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "加熱功能……壞了，等我先修一下……！", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "帕斯卡拉", "content": "嘶……嘶……好冷……"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "帕斯卡拉", "content": "阿啾！"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以煉些簡單的發熱物質，應該不會花太久……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些材料用來修羅盤。取暖的事，我來想辦法。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……阿啾！……阿啾！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……姐姐，能不能再分我一些毯子，我人小，冷得快，真的快要凍死了……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種時候就別什麼你的我的了，都擠到一起！伊西多，別在那邊煩惱了，過來吧！", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "能和我這樣的大帥哥擠在一起……"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "唔！毯子蓋到我的頭了！"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#9$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_L2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜擋在風口，帕斯卡拉被蒂奇包起來，只露出一張被擠成一團的臉。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "極境和溫蒂努力活動著僵硬的手指，好抓起食物送進嘴裡。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多想要轉身回到塑金台，但在拿起探針的那一刻，他意識到，自己凍僵的手指毫無用處。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "征服宣告號漫無目的地順風行駛著。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g8_oldcabin", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……我們現在要往哪裡去？", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，往深處開吧。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道我們要去哪裡……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道那些臭念經的什麼時候會追上來……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不知道這麼冷，我會不會就醒不過來了，或者是船又撞上什麼東西……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4163_rosesa_1#9$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-30", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她怎麼突然變成這樣？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是應該一開始就先搶一個最暖和的位置睡覺了嗎？說不定還會半夜搶走我們所有人的毯子。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也就只是個剛過十歲的小丫頭。", "name": "蒂奇"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1580_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她睡著了，還有點發燒，看看她的口袋裡有沒有什麼能用的草藥。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#12$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是明天我就要死在這裡了……我還、我還想回去我原先的家再睡一覺……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大房子還在……我的床、我的被子、我的浴缸……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿最好看的衣服，一套又一套……！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃不完的食物，花不完的錢，我不用再……被人一腳踢出去……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被人踢好痛……從街這頭滾到街那頭，好痛……我只想回一趟家……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要過上好日子……！", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不要死在……死在……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呼……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕斯卡拉"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒想到這次居然會走到這麼危險的地步……抱歉，溫蒂，我不該輕易地讓你過來……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#2$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我既然來了，就是來幫你們的。", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能平安回到羅德島，我就把我這個月的薪水都賠給你！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，啊哈……我先休息了……", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "好……"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "棘刺？你還在幹嘛？"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修羅盤，不然我們連骸礁峽谷都開不出去。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船上太顛簸了，我需要搭建足夠複雜的法術能量場來穩定心相原質，否則整個羅盤很有可能在我拆解它的那一刻就分崩離析了。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使能夠搭建出這樣的能量場，我也需要確保自己施術的手足夠穩，不會在進行物質重構的過程中出差錯……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果在心相原質內部刻印流體源石迴路的過程中手有一絲顫抖，都可能會廢掉整塊材料……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，極境，我也不確定明天我們是否能夠……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呼……", "name": "極境"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看他那副樣子，應該是累壞了。今天他一直學著掌舵，之前沒做過這種事情吧？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒有，他之前只負責過通訊相關的工作。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也坐過來一點吧，溫度還在下降，擠一擠會暖和一點。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小珍珠，你要不……？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……夫人……", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……夫人……爸爸說你們出海……海真的是藍色的嗎？", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，你們能帶我出海嗎？我覺得我長大了……我也能出海了……！", "name": "蒂奇"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小珍珠？你這是……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#5$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是小時候蒂奇在自己懷裡聽到的故事。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜把手放在蒂奇的額頭上，但現在她的額頭已經爬上了皺紋。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#7$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，蒂奇也發燒了，草藥還有剩下的嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "伊西多", "content": "我找找……"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pcket", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "伊西多", "content": "就這些。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "翻藥聲在船艙內響起，伴隨著睡夢中的人們沉重的呼吸聲。伊西多把鍋架在勉強修好的仿生海龍上，準備燒水熬藥。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡安娜看著船艙內部光禿禿的骨架，眼神柔和，像是想到很美妙的事。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把草藥丟進鍋子裡，因為船的顛簸，鍋子裡還發出了小小的，類似海浪的聲音。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，你見過海嗎？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比天空還要湛藍的海洋，翻著乳白色泡沫的波浪，彷彿能直接劈向我的雲間閃電……", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，要不要和我們一起出海？", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會是個很好的船長。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#3$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在昏暗中，胡安娜的雙眼閃閃發光，骨架間，冰涼的星光透進來。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想要開口回答，但嘴張了張，最終還是沉默了下去。"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們逃來的方向，追兵的火光閃爍。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "…………", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1577_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibbar", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帆布、鱗皮、大量的木材、黃金時代的遺物……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但幾乎完全沒有食物和水。你們確實是走投無路了。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人總是這樣，非要到這種境地，才能明白秩序的可貴。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……或許吧。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對秩序的遵從為你們帶來了食物、清水與居所。別忘了這一點。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的人明白談判是什麼意思，他們會遵守定好的條款。", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯，你會成為一個優秀的私掠首領。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我的引導下。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把這些收繳來的物資清點入庫，那些強盜也要記錄他們的姓名，然後再帶去城鎮邊緣那幾間空著的房子。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路上小心一點，別引起太多鎮民的注意。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有他們設計的那艘能在鹽漠上行進的船，要完好無損地運回來，那是鎮子日後的希望。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了，西爾弗閣下。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。還有什麼要告訴我的嗎？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們事後還是去找了執裁官閣下……但只找到他衣物的殘片。我幫您放在桌上了。", "name": "習武教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後續的事務我會處理。你下去吧，讓我獨自安靜一下。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧，安納斯塔西奧……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原以為你能拯救我們所有人。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你其實只在乎你自己，是嗎？", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "破布上的黑灰弄髒了每天精心擦拭的桌面。西爾弗拿起破布，呆在原地。"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，他還是將那塊破布丟進了壁爐，然後擦拭起那張辦公桌。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一如他每天清晨準時爬上鐘塔，凝視著這座歷經天災與人禍，卻仍屹立不倒的城鎮。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不在乎這個國家，不在乎這座鎮子，不在乎這些人。所以你不會明白，安納斯塔西奧。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊比利亞……不論繁華的商港還是貧瘠的漁村，那些僥倖沒被海洋吞沒的聚落，沒有一座不在混亂中崩潰。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經的雅隆也是如此。是我把半生都投進了這裡，是我把它從同類相食的慘劇和慘無人道的暴政中拯救了出來……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#4$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在也是我為它取得了能行走大地的鹽船，要將它從貧瘠的廢土中解放。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#4$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你，安納斯塔西奧，你只看得見自己偏執而古板的信仰。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你永遠不屬於雅隆，你也永遠不會再干涉雅隆。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的，雅隆。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibbar", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我看看，透過複雜的傳動結構，讓風力來驅動步足裝置行走……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來他們從最開始就沒往陸行艦的方向去想。風力步行機……確實是天才般的想法。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，那個阿戈爾女人，明明有如此才能……", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要打造個三五艘，再加上從海盜那裡繳獲的，就能把雅隆的居民都搬上去。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1583_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾十年了……終於不用再被困在這片養不活任何人的鹽漠。", "name": "西爾弗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1583_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drtywndblw", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_57_i06_1", "style": "cg", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 1.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，哪裡來的怪風。", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_57_i06_1", "style": "cg", "pfrom": "0,0", "pto": "0,-70", "pduration": 2.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "aduration": 1.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_match_unignited", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_57_i06_1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……怎麼回事。", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這屋子漏風了嗎，連火也點不起來。", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾粒微小的火星從火柴頭濺起，轉瞬間又熄滅。"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_match_unignited", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_match_unignited", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1", "delay": 1.2}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_match_unignited", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2", "delay": 2.2}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_match", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "3"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_57_i06_2", "style": "cg", "pfrom": "0,-50", "pto": "0,0", "pduration": 1.5, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 2.0, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.85, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看見纖細的火苗在風中搖曳，忽明忽暗的光在黑暗中暈開。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的眼睛逐漸開始適應，周遭的事物一一在他的視野中浮現。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "57_i06_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，他看見一張臉。鹽一般蒼白的皮膚上，斑駁地掛著赤褐色的血跡，濕漉漉的頭髮像臟器的殘片般無力地垂蕩。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一張死人的臉。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你……你……", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒有人能在經歷過一場那樣的爆炸之後活下來……", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎麼做到的？你、你是什麼東西？", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你初次見到我的時候，我也是受了傷，徒步穿越鹽漠來到了雅隆。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你那時問我的，是我需不需要幫助。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時的你，多麼渴望自己能幫到他人。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "西爾弗"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "57_i06_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在呢？當你一次又一次地阻止教士們來救我，當你肆無忌憚地在內心想像我的死亡……你是在謀求什麼？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也被欲望所腐化了，是嗎？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadswordblood", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_drawer", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_57_i06_2"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有再說任何一句話，西爾弗癱倒下去。他似乎想抓住什麼，卻只是把抽屜拉了出來。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花瓣從抽屜中傾瀉而下，埋住了西爾弗的半個身子。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乾枯的花，腐敗的花，化作黑灰的花。幾年前的花，十幾年前的花，幾十年前的花。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長久以來，鎮民們為表感謝，向他們的證裁官閣下送上的每一朵花，都在此刻傾瀉而下。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……花？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadsword_polish", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "sw", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "sw", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他聽到磨刀的聲音戛然而止。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "門外人聲嘈雜起來，他的母親尖銳地嘶吼著、辯解著，說她磨刀只是為了切菜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但家裡已經很久沒有見過半根菜葉了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你安全了，孩子。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你母親發瘋了，但我們已經控制住她了。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……", "name": "小安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天哪，他在吃什麼……", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！不要！！", "name": "小安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他像母親那樣尖聲嘶吼，胡亂揮舞著雙手，試圖遮掩自己的臉。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他怕教士聞到肉塊的腥味，看到他嘴角沾著的肉屑。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他明明已經下定了決心，要用死亡終結自己這罪孽的存在，為何此刻，面對這位善良的教士，他又要拚命地隱藏自己的惡行？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……", "name": "小安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有罪……讓我死……", "name": "小安納斯塔西奧"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，孩子。你只是想活下去，我不該審判你。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的罪，該由你自己活著贖清。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有罪的人千千萬萬。我們行走大地，就是為了幫那些無力自己贖罪的人，為了祛除他們的罪孽。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也可以這樣做，這樣才能贖清你自己的罪。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終有一日，最純潔的花朵……也會因你的觸摸而綻放。", "name": "審判庭教士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1587_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}